{"tid":2240081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我好撚on9咁接受來歷不明嘅街訪","createTime":"2020-10-12T11:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T15:43:45.000Z","uid":268163,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f5cba54e615a7e9bc5a93616410ca536e731b72","tid":2240081,"uid":268163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"今日去荃灣黃店買嘢飲果陣比人叫住我做個街訪話係問12手足同lunch哥，咁我就問佢地咩機構，佢地話係香港民研，雖然有cam但同我講唔使除罩做，於是我信咗就接受訪問。<br />\n<br />\n一開始問12手足算正常冇乜異樣，跟著問lunch gor嘢問題就開始露餡。佢地係咁問lunch gor係交友app呃蝦條呀，又問我有冇搭黨鐵同點睇lunch gor比人屌分化撚。我先開始覺得唔撚對路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊有自己人會問呢啲撚屌問題，呢間百分百肯定係藍媒紅媒嚟。<br />\n<br />\n奉觀各位手足們唔好好似小弟咁撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係街見到啲自稱黃/唔藍嘅人做訪問除非係最出名果啲，否則真係唔好制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSor for 1999"},{"pid":"0d1a2fac07784f408da249c2680ce6f6159955e2","tid":2240081,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"117e53ac0d6e738341eecd8d3806991825842a95","tid":2240081,"uid":268163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:01:04.000Z","msg":"自推一個"},{"pid":"2f44e5afa8858839df72881fc14b536e6131b735","tid":2240081,"uid":226573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T12:19:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8d5d459524082083361cfe6049809088772c3abe","ti